OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright with plenty of sunshine
OL,7,Fduring this period. Very warm in
OL,8,Fgeneral, but cooler at times along the
OL,9,Feast coast.
